                    <span>Even though I am a Cubs fan, my favorite baseball player is Lou Gehrig. This book has a lot of baseball information that My Luke and I did not have.  <p>If you want to read about Gehrigs baseball career this is a great  book to read.  I suggest if you really want to read about Gehrig get a copy  of My Luke and I By Elenor Gehrig even if it is out of print.</span>
                  
              
